flowchart TD
    RAW["`**Raw Dataset**
    (epoch, sid) from RINEX store`"]

    RAW --> SIG["`**Signal Selection**
    keep_sids filter
    obs type selection`"]

    SIG --> QC["`**Quality Control**
    polar angle cutoff
    SNR threshold mask`"]

    QC --> TA["`**TemporalAggregate**
    resample → regular epoch grid
    configurable window (e.g. 1 min)`"]

    TA --> GA["`**GridAssignment**
    KDTree nearest-cell query
    2° equal-area hemigrid`"]

    GA --> OUT["`**PipelineResult**
    + cell_id coord
    + pipeline metadata attrs`"]

    OUT --> STORE["`**Icechunk Store**
    versioned, atomic commit`"]
